{
  "texts": [
    "For example, a service provider that leverages a foundation model such as Llama2 to offer some service (possibly after some additional fine-tuning) does not have access to the data used by the party that conducted the pre-training.",
    "However, the service provider may still be required by law to fulfill forgetting requests.",
    "For the sake of generality, we will abstain from including D as a parameter for forgetting, although D may be used in some procedures.",
    "When implementing digital forgetting in ML models (and in LLMs in particular), the following requirements should be taken into consideration.",
    "Forgetting guarantees."
  ]
}